"    Another example of a two-piece device, with full occlusal coverage, and a titratable slot and flange coupling mechanism in the vicinity of the posterior teeth, permitting mouth opening and closing whilst in advancement (SomnoMed MAS&reg;, SomnoMed Ltd, Australia).",
"    <div class=\"footnotes\">",
